articles.title: LG visits RVS iGlobal Corporate Office, highlights Jammu’s rise as emerging IT hub
articles.description: Excelsior Correspondent JAMMU, Dec 4: The Lieutenant Governor Manoj Sinha today visited the RVS iGlobal Corporate Office at Narwal, marking a significant milestone in the region’s fast-expanding technology landscape. The visit underscored Jammu’s growing prominence as an emerging IT hub. The LG toured the facility and reviewed key operations, including the company’s fully functional Network Operations Centre (NOC) and Security Operations Centre (SOC). Live demonstrations of cybersecurity workflows, global 24/7 monitoring and managed IT services showcased the organisation’s world-class infrastructure, […]
